  dcterms:isPartOf <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-knowledge-maps/rdf> .
n:cip-1694 gb:externalLink <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-knowledge-maps/rdf/node/cip-1694/link/0> .
