  rdfs:label "contains" ; gb:description """Plutus cost models assign abstract CPU and memory costs to each builtin function, calibrated by benchmarking on a reference machine. These are consensus-critical — every node must compute identical ExUnits. Updates go through the Technical group governance threshold.""" ;
  gb:edgeIndex 35 ; dcterms:isPartOf <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-knowledge-maps/rdf> .

