  rdfs:label "some params are" ; gb:description """Economic security-relevant parameters: txFeePerByte, txFeeFixed, utxoCostPerByte, minFeeRefScriptCostPerByte. Setting these too low enables denial-of-service via cheap spam transactions. SPO approval at Q5 = 51% is required.""" ;
  gb:edgeIndex 37 ; dcterms:isPartOf <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-knowledge-maps/rdf> .

