  rdfs:label "requires" ; gb:description """Submitting a governance action requires 100,000 ada (refundable). This anti-spam mechanism prevents frivolous proposals from flooding the chain. The amount is a Governance group parameter, also classified as security-relevant (requires SPO approval to change).""" ;
  gb:edgeIndex 56 ; dcterms:isPartOf <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-knowledge-maps/rdf> .

